{"product_id":"berrichi-natural-renewal-toner-100ml","title":"BERRICHI Natural Renewal Toner 100ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eBerrichi Facial Toner – an innovative solution for cleansing and renewing the skin. This effective toner removes dirt, excess oil and dead skin cells while gently exfoliating the skin as it helps to remove dead skin cells. Regular use helps to reduce pigmentation, smooth skin texture and restore skin’s natural radiance and elasticity.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eEffectively removes dirt, excess oil and dead skin cells\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eReduces pigmentation\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eProvides even skin tone and a radiant complexion\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSmoothes the surface of the skin and reduces the appearance of roughness\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eAccelerates cell renewal, helping to achieve a fresh and radiant complexion\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eMain ingredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eFurcellaran\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e \u003c\/strong\u003e– antioxidant, helps to maintain skin moisture balance and strengthen the skin’s protective barrier, slows down the skin’s ageing process, reduces inflammation and dryness. Furtsellaran is obtained from algae grown in Estonian waters.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eFruit acids – AHA Phytocomplexon\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003ea blend of effective AHA acids that exfoliate, moisturise, smooth and balance the skin. It is the ideal natural ingredient for exfoliating and cleansing even the most sensitive skin.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSuitable for all skin types.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply the toner to a cotton pad and cleanse face, neck and cleavage. Or apply directly to the skin with your palms. Avoid the eye area. The product may cause a slight tingling sensation on the skin the first few times it is used. Before going out in the sun, it is recommended to apply a cream with a sun protection factor on the skin.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Propanediol, Citric Acid, Lactic Acid, Tartaric Acid, Glucose, Acer Saccharum Extract, Citrus Limon Peel Oil, Glycerin, Mentha Piperita Leaf Extract, Sodium Benzoate, Microcitrus Australasica Fruit Extract, Heptyl Glucoside, Sodium hydroxide, Capryloyl\/Caproyl\/Anhydro, Methyl Glucamide\/Heptyl Glucoside, Potassium Sorbate, Furcellaria Lumbricalis Extract. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Berrichi","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51084152668487,"sku":null,"price":25.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/berrichi-natural-renewal-toner-100ml-370058.png?v=1739979951","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/berrichi-natural-renewal-toner-100ml","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}